<h2 id="conclusion">conclusion</h2>

<p>As you can see, quite the international crowd (also have spoken with people from: Brazil, Sweden, France, Kazakhstan). For me this is the big <em>tell</em> of any successful startup scene: it attracts talent globally.</p>
